---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import Signup from '../components/Signup.astro';
---
<Base title="Newsletter — Kavya" description="One thoughtful email, roughly every other Sunday.">
  <article class="container measure page">
    <span class="eyebrow">The newsletter</span>
    <h1>The best way to follow along.</h1>
    <div class="prose">
      <p>Once every couple of weeks I send a short, personal email: something I learned, something I’m reading, and an honest update on how this site is growing — the wins and the flat months alike.</p>
      <p>It’s the one place I share the behind-the-scenes thinking that doesn’t make it into a full post. No fluff, no daily barrage, unsubscribe in one click.</p>
    </div>
    <Signup />
    <div class="prose">
      <h2>What past issues looked like</h2>
      <p class="muted">Archive coming soon — your first issue will be the welcome email with my three favourite posts.</p>
    </div>
  </article>
</Base>

<style>
  .page { padding-block: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 4rem); }
  .page h1 { margin: 0.5rem 0 1.2rem; }
</style>
